title: SwedishAmerican and Rockford Police Department to Host Strong Neighborhood House Trunk-or-Treat Event (SwedishAmerican Health System ...
text: ( Source : SwedishAmerican Health System Corp) October 7, 2015 SwedishAmerican and the Rockford Police Department are teaming up to host a free Trunk-or-Treat event at the Strong Neighborhood House , located at 1233 Revell Avenue in Rockford.
